04:58.731 --> 05:01.933
<i>an expert on</i>                    
<i>the Israel-Palestine conflict.</i>  

05:02.034 --> 05:05.369
        What makes              
        this uprising different 
        than previous uprisings?

05:05.472 --> 05:08.038
First is the failure            
of the Palestinian leadership   

05:08.140 --> 05:11.008
<i>to do anything to relieve</i>       
<i>the sense of despair</i>            

05:11.110 --> 05:13.511
<i>that Palestinians</i>               
<i>have been feeling</i>               
<i>in the occupied territories</i>     

05:13.613 --> 05:15.613
<i>since the occupation began.</i>     

05:15.715 --> 05:18.583
The prospects                   
for young Palestinians          
are extraordinarily limited.    

05:18.685 --> 05:23.888
No horizon, no future.          
Things are much worse today     
after Oslo.                     

05:23.990 --> 05:27.959
         Shihab-Eldin:          
  <i> In 1993, the Oslo Accords</i>    
    <i> were supposed to begin</i>     

05:28.060 --> 05:31.428
    <i> a path towards peace,</i>      
    <i> and established</i>            
    <i> an interim government</i>      

05:31.531 --> 05:35.733
<i>in the West Bank known</i>          
<i>as the Palestinian Authority.</i>   

05:35.835 --> 05:39.570
   What was the expectation     
   of the Palestinian Authority?

05:39.672 --> 05:41.906
That this was the embryo        
 of a Palestinian state.        

05:42.008 --> 05:45.776
The Oslo agreement was          
supposed to accomplish          
a continued negotiation.        

05:45.879 --> 05:48.479
The hope was that it would      
lead to a two-state solution,   

05:48.581 --> 05:50.648
and the Palestinians could      
have some arrangement           

05:50.750 --> 05:52.750
for autonomy                    
or self-government              
within that.                    

05:52.852 --> 05:55.920
Unfortunately, it's deluding    
very few people in Palestine    

05:56.022 --> 05:58.523
and a lot of people outside     
into thinking the Palestinians  

05:58.625 --> 06:00.958
are well on the way             
to statehood. They're not.      

06:01.060 --> 06:03.928
They've moved away              
from self-determination         
since Oslo.                     

06:04.030 --> 06:07.398
      <i> So, in a sense,</i>          
      <i> the Palestinian Authority</i>
      <i> itself is an illusion?</i>   

06:07.500 --> 06:12.503
It is.                          
