10:28.627 --> 10:30.427
      He just got married,      
       he's moving in now.      

10:30.529 --> 10:32.529
          Shihab-Eldin:         
      <i> But as settlers were</i>     
     <i> moving into one house,</i>    

10:32.631 --> 10:36.500
 <i> we met a Palestinian family</i>   
 <i> that was being evicted</i>        
 <i> from theirs.</i>                  

10:36.602 --> 10:38.869
 (speaking in foreign language) 

