11:11.737 --> 11:14.071
      <i> these settlements</i>        
      <i> as a provocation.</i>        

11:14.173 --> 11:15.940
     <i> But when they clash</i>       
     <i> with settlers,</i>            

11:16.042 --> 11:19.443
<i>Israel escalates its security</i>   
<i>measures across the region.</i>     

11:19.545 --> 11:22.980
      <i> Nowhere is this</i>          
